@c_vaughn22 is NOBULL. We're excited to welcome Running Back Deuce Vaughn to Team NOBULL. We're just days away from watching Deuce showcase all of the work he has put in to prepare for the NFL Combine presented by NOBULL.

Hear more from Deuce on what it means to join Team NOBULL and how he's approaching the next chapter of his career as a running back:

“Hardwork. A trait that was introduced to me at a very young age. It has been the backbone of every accomplishment and accolade I have received. Understanding that the process is much more important than the result. The way that I work in the dark will give me the opportunity to be successful when the lights shine the brightest. 

Too Small. These two words have followed me throughout my entire career. Instead of allowing it to deter me, I flipped the script and used it as fuel. Deemed as a weakness and a flaw I have now turned into my ‘superpower.’

Just the beginning. As I embark on this next step of my football career, the mission remains the same. Continue to prove the doubters wrong, through my hard work and process-driven mindset, while also using my platform to inspire young athletes that are just like I was. Doubted and counted out. That’s why #IAMNOBULL.“ - @c_vaughn22

#TrainingIsEverything
